cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image inpainting, which is a common task in computer vision.
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a generative model based on gated convolutions learned from millions of images.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper presents a system that can automatically complete images with free-form masks and guidance.
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with modifying image layouts and removing distracting objects.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image editing and manipulation.
